data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER: Come see this move-in ready 4 bedroom home in the mature Cedar Glen neighborhood. The welcoming entry connects to a comfortable living room with a large bay window and flows nicely into the dining area. The kitchen features a large double sink, real wood cabinetry, and stainless steel Samsung appliances. The 2nd living room has a cozy wood burning fireplace and sliding doors that lead to a large covered patio. Relax in the hot tub while enjoying the view of the spacious fully-fenced backyard! The primary bedroom connects to an ensuite that includes double sinks, walk-in shower, and skylights! This home is close to Hillcrest Elementary, Oak Harbor High School, and a 5 minute drive from NAS Whidbey and town. Come see today!
